OL,6,FFellow survivor, Wayne Birkett says
OL,7,F"The whole system feels broken. From
OL,8,Fthe lack of money to fund mental
OL,9,Fhealth services, to the broken lines
OL,10,Fof communication between all the
OL,11,Forganisations who had contact with
OL,12,FCalocane.
OL,14,F"The government needs to make sure
OL,15,Fthat there is enough money and
OL,16,Fresources available to make the
OL,17,Fchanges needed to protect the people
OL,18,Fof Nottingham."
