OL,3,C'System feels broken': Survivors speak
OL,4,Cout as Nottingham inquiry moves closer
OL,6,FValdo Calocane killed students Barnaby
OL,7,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,8,F19, and caretaker Ian Coates, 65,
OL,9,Fbefore attempting to kill three other
OL,10,Fpeople in the city in June 2023.
OL,12,FThe inquiry aims to report back within
OL,13,Ftwo years with recommendations to
OL,14,Fprevent similar incidents, the
OL,15,FMinistry of Justice (MoJ) said.
OL,17,FWitnesses from Nottinghamshire Police
OL,18,Fand the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,19,F(CPS) could be compelled to give
OL,20,Fevidence, the Government said on
OL,21,FThursday.
