OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) previously prepared a
OL,8,Freport which concluded that officers
OL,9,Ffailed to properly investigate an
OL,10,Fassault on warehouse workers by
OL,11,FCalocane which could have stopped his
OL,12,Fmurder spree a month later.
OL,14,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,15,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,16,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,17,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,18,Fattempted murder ` something which has
OL,19,Fbeen widely criticised by the victims'
OL,20,Ffamilies.
