OL,6,FThe MoJ said the management of
OL,7,FCalocane's risk to others in the lead-
OL,8,Fup to the attacks and public servants
OL,9,Faccessing information without
OL,10,Fauthorisation will form part of the
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FThe victims' families previously said
OL,14,Fclaims that healthcare staff illegally
OL,15,Faccessed medical records belonging to
OL,16,Ftheir loved ones were "sickening" and
OL,17,F"inexcusable".
