OL,6,FThree Nottinghamshire Police officers
OL,7,Falso faced disciplinary action for
OL,8,Fviewing material about the case
OL,9,Fwithout any legitimate reason, and
OL,10,Fthere have been alleged data breaches
OL,11,Fby staff working for HM Prison and
OL,12,FProbation Service and HM Courts and
OL,13,FTribunals Service.
OL,15,FEmergency services staff who responded
OL,16,Fto the attacks will also be
OL,17,Fscrutinised by the inquiry as part of
OL,18,Fa "detailed examination" of events on
